{
  "stem": "11744.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were protected by that already, but if there was anyone who was asking a question about strange people-- I mean, they don't belong here.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Who are they-- The priest was always putting his foot down and--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wish I would.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really wish I would, because he could be about-- about-- about the Gentiles who have helped the Jews, because he was wonderful, absolutely wonderful.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Izeaux.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Izeaux-- a little town near Grenoble.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A bicycle.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't ask me again to ride a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never could.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we had miles and miles and miles of bicycle-- whenever I went up in the mountain to get some food, whenever we see the-- the peasant didn't have any ration, any coupon-- we had them, but not the peasant, because they were having cultivating their own food, so they weren't getting anything else.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the food that we get on coupon they didn't get.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They weren't making that, so if we could give them some of our coupon, they would give me six eggs, maybe.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Suddenly we had a head of six eggs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so that bicycle was very important.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then when my children need to go to a dentist, I had to go 40 miles to the town, to Grenoble, and put them on my bicycle and go and take them to the dentist.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, I mean, you know, the children really lived with fear all the time, because they were going to school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Germans were coming into school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was one of their big device.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they would very nice and very smiley and then talk to the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would, for instance, say, everybody here goes to Sunday school?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And who here doesn't go to Sunday school?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
